@node HISTORY "History"
---<History>---

  v1.0 ... Internal Release
  v1.1 ... Internal Release 
             Fixed Timing problem, 
             changed file axs to save memory!!
  v1.2 ... Beta Release
             Major change to log.data axs - much improved speed:-)
             Added auto-skip if log.data empty.
             Lots of code optimisation - how tedious!!
  v1.3 ... First General Release - 28 Jan 1999
             Added PerCent proofing.
  v1.4 ... 2nd General Release - 01 Feb 1999
             Fixed the wrap-around problem with Log.data :-))
              (Anthony Barrett must have been having a bad day!!)



